dct_title_s: Mapa de codificacion postal : ciudad de la Habana
dct_description_sm: On recto: map shows postal codes, numbers of postal zones, post offices, provincial and municipal limits, bridges, and dams. On verso: map shows Havana city center in greater detail.
dct_creator_sm: Cuba. Instituto Cubano de Geodesia y Cartografía, issuing body
dct_publisher_sm: Habana, Cuba : Instituto Cubano de Geodesia y Cartografía, 1988.
